{"items":[{"term":"拍殕仔光","pronunciation":"phah-phú-á-kng","definition":"名詞。破曉、天剛亮的微光時刻，日出之前天色由暗轉灰的短暫過渡。","fieldNote":"竹林在山腰。阿公挖筍一定是拍殕仔光就出門，說天一亮筍仔就出青，出了青就老了。小時候跟過一次，天還沒亮，路是黑的，竹葉的聲音很大。阿公蹲下去的樣子像在跟地在說話。筍挖起來帶著泥，很冷，他用衫角擦了一下，塞進麻袋。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/4102/","imageAlt":"拍殕仔光","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/618b362f812948b7-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/618b362f812948b7-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/618b362f812948b7-480.webp 480w, assets/images/618b362f812948b7-768.webp 768w, assets/images/618b362f812948b7-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/618b362f812948b7-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"菁仔欉","pronunciation":"tshenn-á-tsâng","definition":"名詞。①檳榔樹。②比喻莽撞、冒失、突然出現讓人不知所措的人。","fieldNote":"阿嬤家巷口有個男生，每次騎車過來都直接衝進院子，煞不住才停，碎石子被輪子帶起來灑一地。進門也不敲，一腳踢開紗門，站在客廳喊「阿姨我來矣」，帶著一股汗臭和太陽的氣味。阿嬤說他是菁仔欉，但每次他來都把他餵飽才趕走。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/8908/","imageAlt":"菁仔欉","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/c9b5a6bee02706d0-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/c9b5a6bee02706d0-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/c9b5a6bee02706d0-480.webp 480w, assets/images/c9b5a6bee02706d0-768.webp 768w, assets/images/c9b5a6bee02706d0-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/c9b5a6bee02706d0-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"紅絳絳","pronunciation":"âng-kòng-kòng","definition":"形容詞。紅彤彤。形容顏色極紅。","fieldNote":"表哥第一次帶女朋友回家吃飯，阿嬤從廚房出來看了一眼，走回去之前說了一句什麼。他站在那裡，臉就紅絳絳了。我問他阿嬤說什麼，他說沒有啦。問了三次都說沒有。後來聽大人講，阿嬤說的是「媠，有夠媠。」","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/5417/","imageAlt":"紅絳絳","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/961f566af1ebb30f-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/961f566af1ebb30f-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/961f566af1ebb30f-480.webp 480w, assets/images/961f566af1ebb30f-768.webp 768w, assets/images/961f566af1ebb30f-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/961f566af1ebb30f-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"暗摸摸","pronunciation":"àm-bong-bong","definition":"形容詞。形容光線不明亮、陰暗漆黑的樣子。","fieldNote":"小時候去阿嬤家，她的儲藏室從來不開燈。她用手就能找到要的東西——醬油在左邊第二格，米袋靠牆，鹽巴放地上。有一次我跟進去，她說暗摸摸的你囡仔莫亂動。我站在門口，看她的手在黑暗裡翻找，像是黑暗對她沒有效。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/27376/","imageAlt":"暗摸摸","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/5fc302f0aa2405b6-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/5fc302f0aa2405b6-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/5fc302f0aa2405b6-480.webp 480w, assets/images/5fc302f0aa2405b6-768.webp 768w, assets/images/5fc302f0aa2405b6-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/5fc302f0aa2405b6-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"毋甘","pronunciation":"m̄-kam","definition":"動詞／形容詞。捨不得；不忍心；對某人或某物有深切愛惜而不願耗用或失去。","fieldNote":"媽媽有一瓶香水，是美國阿姨探親那年帶回來的。放在梳妝台最裡面的抽屜，開過幾次，每次開了又蓋回去。我問她為什麼不用，她說「毋甘」。\n\n阿姨後來就沒有再回來了。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/879/","imageAlt":"毋甘","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/46adb7aa09a635cc-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/46adb7aa09a635cc-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/46adb7aa09a635cc-480.webp 480w, assets/images/46adb7aa09a635cc-768.webp 768w, assets/images/46adb7aa09a635cc-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/46adb7aa09a635cc-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"拍損","pronunciation":"phah-sńg","definition":"動詞。使物件毀壞；浪費（物力、食物、時間）；糟蹋。","fieldNote":"阿嬤從廚房探出頭，看我把吃剩的便當倒進廚餘桶，皺著眉說「拍損」。不是罵，是疼。那種疼裡面，有她整個年代。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/4119/","imageAlt":"拍損","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/749c73b758574876-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/749c73b758574876-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/749c73b758574876-480.webp 480w, assets/images/749c73b758574876-768.webp 768w, assets/images/749c73b758574876-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/749c73b758574876-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"好玄","pronunciation":"hònn-hiân","definition":"形容詞。對於不了解的事物感到新奇，產生興趣或想進一步探究。","fieldNote":"小時候颱風天停電，阿公點蠟燭。火苗在風中晃，把每個人影投在牆上像皮影戲。我蹲在桌腳，伸手去碰我自己的影子。影子也伸手。我把手放遠一點，影子變大；放近，變小。阿公在旁邊笑說「囡仔人就是好玄」。風還在叫，但我已經忘了害怕。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/14002/","imageAlt":"好玄","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/e0a26e22482c86d9-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/e0a26e22482c86d9-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/e0a26e22482c86d9-480.webp 480w, assets/images/e0a26e22482c86d9-768.webp 768w, assets/images/e0a26e22482c86d9-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/e0a26e22482c86d9-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"數念","pronunciation":"siàu-liām","definition":"動詞。想念、掛念、懷念。","fieldNote":"姑姑嫁去日本十年了。每次打電話回來，阿嬤從來不主動講「我想妳」。她講菜市場誰誰誰漲價、隔壁的狗生了幾隻、今年的芒果收得好。講完一輪才說「恁彼爿會寒無？」掛電話以後，她在客廳坐很久。沒有開電視。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/11122/","imageAlt":"數念","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/ccefcae19e269940-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/ccefcae19e269940-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/ccefcae19e269940-480.webp 480w, assets/images/ccefcae19e269940-768.webp 768w, assets/images/ccefcae19e269940-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/ccefcae19e269940-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"月眉","pronunciation":"gue̍h-bâi","definition":"名詞。農曆初三、初四的新月，形狀彎細像眉毛，故名月眉。","fieldNote":"山上的家，門口就是石階一階一階往下走。晚上吃完飯，阿公會帶我站在最高那一階乘涼。山風從谷底吹上來。他抬手往對面山稜線一指，說「彼叫月眉」。一道細細的鉤掛在山頂上。我以為月亮只有一種——圓的。原來它也會慢慢長大，從一道眉毛開始。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/998/","imageAlt":"月眉","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/2129ffa14eddd733-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/2129ffa14eddd733-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/2129ffa14eddd733-480.webp 480w, assets/images/2129ffa14eddd733-768.webp 768w, assets/images/2129ffa14eddd733-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/2129ffa14eddd733-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}}]}
